document.bodyMd:
# RESOLUTION OF {{entity.legalName}}

**ID:** {{resolutionId}}

Adopted on **{{date | longDate}}**.

Resolved, that **{{entity.legalName}}**, a {{entity.jurisdiction}} entity (EIN {{entity.ein}}), shall open a **{{accountType}}** account with **{{bankName}}**.

**Purpose:** {{purpose}}

**Authorized Signers:**
{{#each signingAuthority}}
- {{this.name}}, {{this.title}}
{{/each}}

{{#if limits}}
**Transaction Limits:** {{limits}}
{{/if}}

Any prior resolutions that conflict with the foregoing are hereby revoked.

{{#each signingAuthority}}
---
**{{this.name}}**  
{{this.title}}  
{{this.signatureBlock}}
{{/each}}
